  "texts": [
    "According to Unilever's chief information officer, its use of Gen AI has reduced the amount of time customer agents spend on responses by approximately 90% (Olavsrud, 2023).",
    "Walmart similarly used Gen AI to create a chatbot to execute marketing negotiations with vendors, most of which indicated that they preferred working with the chatbot, which also delivered 3% cost savings (Hoek et al., 2022).",
    "As these use cases illustrate, the impact of Gen AI is significant; it is estimated to exceed $1.3 trillion by 2032 due to its potential to disrupt and change multiple businesses (Bloomberg, 2023).",
    "Herein, we aim to: (1) distinguish Generative AI (Gen AI) from other forms of AI while highlighting its benefits, (2) identify key considerations for practitioners when implementing Gen AI, and (3) explain potential negative consequences of strategic misalignment in the selection of Gen AI tools.",
    "The key contribution is a four-quadrant framework that helps select Gen AI tools based on input type and the level of human modification needed."
  ],
